      passage: `<p>Newly built in 1889, the Eiffel Tower of Paris, France, drew criticism&mdash;even protest&mdash;for the novelty of its unusual spire-like outline. ______ the design feels commonplace, turning up everywhere from a replica Eiffel Tower in Brazil&rsquo;s Rio de Janeiro to structures such as the Copenhagen Zoo Tower, over in Denmark.</p>`,
